channel.title: Where Should I Put Codes?
channel.description:
Ok, I am brand new to this, seriously new to this and I need to find out where to put codes.
I search everywhere but I am not sure where I actually put codes to make it happen lol
I was also wondering how you make people spawn somewhere, like in RS you log in and you go to Lumbridge, I want mine in Varrok.
Thank you! By the way, I am working on a project and I know a lot of you people are amazing at this stuff, and I was wondering if someone could be co-creator, just PM me okie dokie
Thank you so very much!
